		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe try to use an exponential curve between them instead of a linear blend? e.g. <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LKnqECcg6Gw" class="postlink">gamma correct blending</a>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
